<b>Example 1</b>
<br>
Write the following numbers in words;
<br>
(i) 527. 
<br>
(ii) 7 349.
<br>
(iii) 8 129 820.
<br> 
(iv) 19 803 744 310.
<br>
(v) 6 401 000 000 000.
<br>
<b>Solution</b>
<br>
(i)	527 => <b>five hundred and twenty-seven.</b>
<br>
(ii)	7 349 => <b>seven thousand, three hundred and forty-nine.</b>
<br>
(iii)	8 129 820 => <b>eight million, one hundred and twenty-nine thousand, eight hundred and twenty.</b>
<br>
(iv)	19 803 744 310 => 
<b>
nineteen billion, eight hundred and three million, 
seven hundred and forty-four thousand, three hundred and ten.
</b>
<br>
(v)	6 401 000 000 000 => <b>six trillion, four hundred and one billion.</b>
</article>

